sheep.collision
Class Quad

java.lang.Object
  sheep.collision.Quad
All Implemented Interfaces:
SpriteContainer
public class Quad
extends java.lang.Object
implements SpriteContainer

The node in the QuadTree. Each Quad contains four other Quads (unless it is a root node).

Creates a new Quad, and possibly four child Quads (and so on).

Parameters:
tree - The parent tree.
xmin - The lower boundary on the x-axis.
xmax - The upper boundary on the x-axis.
ymin - The lower boundary on the y-axis.
ymax - The upper boundary on the y-axis.
depth - The number of recursion steps. When this hits 0 we're at a child node.

Checks whether this Quad fully contains the BoundingBox.
